    "en": {
      "title": "Party Leaders to meet today (30)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A special meeting of the Committee on Parliamentary Business will be held on Thursday (30) led by Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena with the participation of party leaders.",
        "Parliament Serjeant-at-Arms Narendra Fernando said that party leaders will meet at the Parliament complex at 11.00 AM this morning.",
        "Last week, Parliament was limited to two days due to the fuel crisis.",
        "The entire day on 4th July has been set aside for questions raised by Members of Parliament awaiting oral answers.",
        "Quick Passports for Foreign Employment: Dhammika makes first move as Minister",
        "\u2018List from higher-up\u2019 to issue fuel for luxury SUVs from Kolonnawa Terminal"
      ],
